sbp.mag module¶

Magnetometer (mag) messages.

class sbp.mag.MsgMagRaw(sbp=None, **kwargs)[source]¶

Bases: sbp.msg.SBP

SBP class for message MSG_MAG_RAW (0x0902).

You can have MSG_MAG_RAW inherit its fields directly from an inherited SBP object, or construct it inline using a dict of its fields.

Raw data from the magnetometer.

sbp
: SBP
SBP parent object to inherit from.
tow

Milliseconds since start of GPS week. If the high bit is set, the

time is unknown or invalid.

mag_z

Magnetic field in the body frame Z axis
sender

Optional sender ID, defaults to SENDER_ID (see sbp/msg.py).
